

                           [help wield]
-----------------------=========+=========-----------------------                             

Usage: wield <weapon>

  This command will ready a weapon in your inventory for use in
 fighting. This command will wield the first weapon of the type
 chosen that appears in your inventory.  You must use 'unwield'
 if you are already wielding a weapon of the same type you wish
 to wield.  Example: wield sword
             
